        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Our sublimated volleyball jerseys start from surprisingly competitive pricing — get a free quote to compare.</p>
        <a href="/request-a-quote/" class="btn-primary">Request a Free Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

